OL,3,CQuestions turn to Estyn in Wales'
OL,4,Creading debate
OL,6,FThe Welsh government has faced growing
OL,7,Fscrutiny over the way children are
OL,8,Ftaught to read in Wales after an ITV
OL,9,FNews investigation last year found
OL,10,Fthat primary schools were using
OL,11,Fdiscredited methods to teach reading.
OL,13,FNow attention has turned to the
OL,14,Fschools' watchdog that inspects those
OL,15,Fclassrooms, Estyn.
OL,17,FWhat Estyn says it believes
