OL,6,FWhen ITV News asked Estyn which meta-
OL,7,Fanalyses he meant, the inspectorate
OL,8,Fsent one that, in fact, does not
OL,9,Fendorse cueing.
OL,11,FIn its written responses to questions,
OL,12,FEstyn has many times reiterated that
OL,13,Fit does not endorse one approach but
OL,14,Finstead promotes what it calls a
OL,15,F"balanced" model of teaching reading.
OL,17,FI wrote about what a "balanced
OL,18,Fapproach" means here.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@JO]yD@VOUzD@IO]
