OL,6,FHowever, that view (that phonics
OL,7,Fshould be mixed with other strategies
OL,8,Ffor decoding words) is not supported
OL,9,Fby scientific consensus on how
OL,10,Fchildren learn to read, which finds
OL,11,Fthat combining approaches can slow
OL,12,Fchildren's progress.
OL,14,FWho gets to influence inspectors?
