OL,6,FIt has since emerged that Estyn also
OL,7,Finvited Professor Dominic Wyse, one of
OL,8,Fthe Welsh government's Expert Literacy
OL,9,FPanel members, who has questioned the
OL,10,Fevidence for giving phonics such a
OL,11,Fcentral role in early reading, to
OL,12,Fpresent to all Estyn staff and
OL,13,Finspectors on how reading should be
OL,14,Ftaught.
OL,16,FProfessor Wyse is an education
OL,17,Facademic specialising in curriculum
OL,18,Fand literacy policy.
