OL,6,FWhen she followed up her first email,
OL,7,Fwhich was ignored, she was
OL,8,Faccidentally copied into an internal
OL,9,FEstyn email that described her as
OL,10,F"evangelical about a single approach",
OL,11,Fbut that by meeting her, "at least
OL,12,Fwe'll have given her air time."
OL,14,FMrs Nonweiler was later invited to
OL,15,Fmeet privately with senior staff, but
OL,16,Fwas not allowed to address inspectors
OL,17,Fdirectly.
