OL,6,FMrs Nonweiler told ITV News the
OL,7,Fcomments suggest that Estyn "views
OL,8,Fthose who recommend systematic
OL,9,Fsynthetic phonics as ideologically
OL,10,Fdriven, rather than guided by
OL,11,Fextensive research and teaching
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"That's concerning. It reveals a
OL,15,Fpreconception that undermines evidence-
OL,16,Fbased practice."
