OL,6,FEstyn has apologised for the internal
OL,7,Femail and confirmed it was sent in
OL,8,Ferror.
OL,10,FOn why she was not invited to speak to
OL,11,Finspectors, Estyn said: "From time to
OL,12,Ftime, Estyn invites external speakers
OL,13,Fto present to our inspectors as part
OL,14,Fof their continuing professional
OL,15,Fdevelopment.
OL,17,F"At the time, we had a focus on
OL,18,Fliteracy and Professor Wyse had
OL,19,Fpublished the largest meta-analysis of
OL,20,Freading studies and was therefore
OL,21,Finvited to share the findings."
