OL,6,FThe watchdog added that it shares Mrs
OL,7,FNonweiler's and the Welsh government's
OL,8,Fconcerns about reading standards in
OL,9,FWales and is planning "an enhanced
OL,10,Ffocus on reading within our inspection
OL,11,Fframework for the next three years".
OL,13,FHowever, Estyn has not identified
OL,14,Fmajor weaknesses in early reading.
OL,15,FInstead, the inspectorate says the
OL,16,Fbigger challenge lies in the
OL,17,Ftransition from primary to secondary
OL,18,Fschool, where many pupils fail to
OL,19,Fdevelop more advanced reading and
OL,20,Fcomprehension skills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
