OL,6,FWhy this matters
OL,8,FThe row over reading methods is not
OL,9,Fjust academic. Decisions made by Estyn
OL,10,Fand the Welsh government shape how
OL,11,Fthousands of children in Wales are
OL,12,Ftaught one of the most important
OL,13,Fskills a school can teach.
OL,15,FAt least one school inspection report,
OL,16,Fwhich has been published since our
OL,17,Finvestigation aired, appears to
OL,18,Fcriticise a school for not teaching
OL,19,Fchildren to use cues to read
OL,20,Funfamiliar words.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
